# 🛡️ Daily Quest Tracker

**An RPG-style app where users complete daily tasks (quests) and earn XP to level up.**  
This gamified routine builder encourages consistent habit formation in a fun, rewarding way.

---
## Part A: Why This App?

This app merges two of my core interests: **gaming and personal productivity**.  
By turning daily responsibilities into quests, it transforms mundane habits into exciting challenges—rewarding consistency and encouraging growth over time.

